OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy but dry start to the
OL,6,Fmorning, with cloud breaking through
OL,7,Fthe late morning and the afternoon
OL,8,Fwith long sunny spells developing.
OL,9,FWinds mainly light and variable.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FCoastal cloud will move
OL,12,Finland giving a cloudy but dry evening
OL,13,Facross the region. Winds light and
OL,14,Fvariable but breezy along the coast.
OL,15,
OL,16,CTuesday:FA cloudy and dry start to the
OL,17,Fday, sunny spells start to develop
OL,18,Fduring the afternoon with clear skies
OL,19,Fovernight. Winds remain light and
OL,20,Fbreezy along the coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
