OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,6,FRemaining very warm with light winds.
OL,7,FVariable amounts of cloud but plenty
OL,8,Fof sunny or clear spells. Most parts
OL,9,Fdry though an isolated shower can't be
OL,10,Fruled out.
